chemaxon.marvin.plugin
Interface LicenseFieldHandler

public interface LicenseFieldHandler

License field handler interface. Parameter panel components containg a license field should implement this to enable the central handling of the license field depending on user license settings.

Version:
Marvin 4.0
Author:
Nora Mate

verify

public java.lang.String verify()
Verifies parameters. Returns the error message on error, null on success. The license item sets the license in the plugin if the field contains a non-empty string. Returns null if either the field is empty or the license key is successfully set.

Returns:
the error message on error, null on success
